▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀
*/

*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*
Static Function fGravaLog(cTEXTO)
*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*
Local cSTR := TIME()+" - "+cTEXTO+CHR(13)+CHR(10)

	fWrite(nHldLOG,cSTR,Len(cSTR))

Return
